Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树林那边的巴士站深处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 就是登上坡道后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位于前方的古老白色公馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说有一个长发的幽灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在着发之女王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是杀人魔一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咔嚓 咔嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想剪断啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的手把那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我要收拾掉所有胆敢扰乱这种关系的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能做到的话 那该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是 做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是光想想就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头…头发 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 刚才的是…对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是灰村切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我偶然坐错了从学校回家的巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个长发的女幽灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不小心回想起了那种传言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.95,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是可疑分子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.55,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫灰村切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过传言倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿急救箱 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发拖到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我替你捧起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪…剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请相信我 我是无意识中拿出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来 从来没有在人前拿出来过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把剪刀 很早之前就一直在家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候 我会用这把剪刀替人剪发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人们也非常开心的让我替他们剪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大家逐渐开始去理发店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌我再去替他们剪发了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要剪头发的冲动 却依然很强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是直到现在兴趣也未曾改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 所以才对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我觉得自己能够理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想给你剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 可以吗 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？真的真的？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.85,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…剪不断的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从出生之后 头发一次都没有剪过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？咦？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这把也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么剪不断啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是武者小路祝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明名字是「祝福」来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:05:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这头长发哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切…真是个奇怪的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算剪不断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕光是抚摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病院坂学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个人刚才在温室那边受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以替他贴了创口贴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了一般人别随便进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活用品我就放这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和我这就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那个人并没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等 我拿外套
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛 那两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人是杀人魔！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准确的说 是杀人魔的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们持有祖传的杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们都是那个恐怖组织的成员 正监视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 她不是看了什么漫画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不信啊 但是她说的一本正经的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子早就举目无亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正被某个团体保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 被害妄想症？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很早就失去了母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲也在几年前死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到她的头发了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子被诅咒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她走得太近 你也会没命的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 小切 你的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是摔了一跤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时至今日 当我看到女生的乌黑长发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是忍不住好想好想去剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定再也不花心了 有小祝在 要对她一心一意！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪不断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发是女人的生命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺滑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不合拍啊 灰村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前一提到头发你就举止怪异起来多有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这说明我已经长大成人了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 高高在上的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 受欢迎的家伙就是不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 我可是第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁班的病院坂 来问了灰村的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个 那个人给我感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是连人都要杀一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校生活好像很愉快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我只上过小学低年级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 就因为这头发 被人嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时不时 会做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦到我拥有普通的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校 和朋友聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新开张的糕点店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅气的明星等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 终究是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究只是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想剪掉它？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说「头发是女人的生命」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在一定范围内生长的话 或许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我的头发 只是不断地变长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是生命 我希望现在就杀了它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是已经给过你忠告了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这个人在一起 只会变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 让我很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的父亲 已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被你们杀了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.25,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用杀害遗品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.21,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(618,660)}Killing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来这家伙是代替你父亲的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺会见风使舵的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能做出那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦 自己一个人去忍受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的重负 不要让别人来担
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发之女王！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你灰村切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果都这么说了你还继续跟她来往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们之间一定会决一死战的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 搞什么 这两个家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们持有祖传的杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.74,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害遗品？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 小切 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是死了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样的人 像我这样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做什么 剪不断你头发的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了小切 你做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 和爷爷没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是…因为你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是从铁四郎那里听说的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近没跟爸爸打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啦到底是什么事 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的祖先出现过一个砍人的杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是说你的名字不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是担心你知道这件事会不会伤心才一直没说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会因为这点事就消沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H0F00E6&\bord0\be1\fs70\frz351.3\pos(436,226)}杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H0F00E6&\bord0\be1\fs70\frz351.3\pos(954,336)}诺马·格雷兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF9761B&\bord0\be1\fs60\frz349.6\pos(480,636)}地下室的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有听说过这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还有以此为原型拍成过电影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个著名的猎奇杀人事件的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把人搬到名为手术室的地下室里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其剪裁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分尸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他使用的凶器虽然众说纷纭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:17:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但普遍认为是一把小型的前端呈锯齿形的剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手持祖传的杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望现在就杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.77,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害遗品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.13,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害遗品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤独的活着 孤独的死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是正确的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即便如此也有人愿意陪在我身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才正望着月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有人要来杀我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我来杀你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是被小切杀死的话 或许也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得白天说过的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的头发是剪不断的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对不死的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀不死的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被诅咒了的…头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把剪刀说不定也被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小祝有说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人魔的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有这可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只有这把剪刀还没试过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我剪掉你的头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.68,english,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,660)}长发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长发大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 如果是诅咒再称其为上帝就太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能剪断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fr270\fs80\c&H010101&\bord0\fsp30\pos(706,368)}拜托了··
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪断了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 剪断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的剪断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如获新生的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切是第一个杀死我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫它罪恶剪刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪恶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是杀了至今为止的我的罪恶剪刀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫这名字行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正大家都受到了诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用起什么漂亮名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪裁并分离的罪恶剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断裁分离的罪恶剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好 罪恶剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖孩子乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也请多关照啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是我在用它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请来剪断吧 我的小切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会这么处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断裁分离的罪恶剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一话 异端的肖像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:39.88,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}窓を開けて見上げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:46.41,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あ　細い三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:52.53,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ガラス細工のように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:59.13,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}煌くひかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:05.75,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}月よ　世界が消えるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:12.33,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}伝えて　いつか出会う一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:19.11,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここで私は待ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:24.96,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}闇にほしかえて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:31.77,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ずっと　My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:35.74,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}願いを届け　星も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:39.05,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}何が起ころうと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:45.17,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君に会える時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:48.93,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}透き通った孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:52.32,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}胸に抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:58.01,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:09.95,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}心から応援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:25.03,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}浅い眠りの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:31.59,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}不思議な夢見た
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:38.07,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君に守られていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:44.38,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}月影の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:51.03,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}どんな運命 巡っても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:57.45,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}必ず君と出会うために
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:22:59.47,IN_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:39.88,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}推开窗户仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:46.41,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}啊 挂着细长的新月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:52.53,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}如玻璃工艺品般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:59.13,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:05.75,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}明月啊 如果世界要消亡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:12.33,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}请转达某一刻将出现的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:19.11,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:24.96,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}即使星空再变换
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:31.77,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}永远都是 My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:35.74,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}请传达我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:39.05,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}连星星也按耐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:45.17,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}直到与你相见之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:48.93,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}将清澈透明的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:52.32,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}紧紧抱在胸前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:58.01,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}呼唤着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:09.95,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}打心底为你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:25.03,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}浅睡之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:31.59,IN_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一场不可思议的梦
